    "description": "Celebrate Burns Night with a vegetarian twist on Scotland's classic national dish, haggis. To make the king of puds, you'll marry mushrooms and lentils with fragrant allspice and black pepper. Serve with parsnip and potato mash and a rich onion gravy. Under 600 calories.",
